OL,7,FOfficials estimate each check to be
OL,8,Fthe equivalent of an NHS appointment
OL,9,Fand will help free up time and cut
OL,10,Fwaiting lists.
OL,12,FWorkers will provide information which
OL,13,Fwill be used to determine their risk
OL,14,Fof developing cardiovascular disease,
OL,15,Fwhich can cause heart attacks, heart
OL,16,Ffailures and stroke.
OL,18,FPlans for a digital version of the NHS
OL,19,FHealth Check have also been announced,
OL,20,Fin a bid to make the programme more
OL,21,Faccessible.
