OL,7,FHealth Minister Andrew Gwynne said:
OL,8,F"This innovative new programme is an
OL,9,Fimportant step towards community-
OL,10,Ffocused healthcare and supporting
OL,11,Feconomic productivity through
OL,12,Fimproving health"
OL,14,FHe added: "We know so many deadly
OL,15,Fdiseases can be avoided if we seek
OL,16,Fhelp in enough time.
OL,18,F"That's why we're working to improve
OL,19,Faccess to treatment while also taking
OL,20,Fsteps to address the preventable
OL,21,Fcauses of cardiovascular disease.
