OL,7,FThe NHS Health Check programme was
OL,8,Fintroduced in 2009 and is offered to
OL,9,Fpeople between the ages of 40 and 79
OL,10,Fevery five years.
OL,12,FThe government has also announced
OL,13,Fplans for a digital version of the
OL,14,Fcheck, which will be available on the
OL,15,FNHS app.
OL,17,FThe platform will allow people to
OL,18,Fprovide information from their home,
OL,19,Fwith the results automatically written
OL,20,Fback into their GP electronic health
OL,21,Frecord.
