OL,7,FTesting of the digital programme will
OL,8,Ftake place in 2025, and councils in
OL,9,FNorfolk, Medway and Lambeth, London,
OL,10,Fsigned up for the trial.
OL,12,FIt is estimated the digital initiative
OL,13,Fwill deliver one million checks in its
OL,14,Ffirst four years, with plans under way
OL,15,Fto roll it out nationally alongside
OL,16,Fface-to-face checks.
