OL,7,FLouise Gittins, chairwoman of the
OL,8,FLocal Government Association, added:
OL,9,F"Health checks can save lives. They
OL,10,Fcan prevent people from developing
OL,11,Flargely preventable diseases, such as
OL,12,Fheart disease, cancer, Type 2 diabetes
OL,13,Fand liver disease.
OL,15,F"Councils are exploring new ways to
OL,16,Fboost uptake, targeting individuals or
OL,17,Fcommunities at increased risk, and
OL,18,Fusing proactive outreach programmes to
OL,19,Fget into those communities who are
OL,20,Fless likely to attend their general
OL,21,Fpractice.
